Buffalo Chicken Burger

25 min
$12
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyWheat

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickSpicyGrilled

Description

A spicy and tangy burger that brings the heat with a delicious creamy sauce, perfect for a hearty meal.

Ingredients

  • ground chicken: 1 pound
  • burger buns: 4
  • buffalo sauce: 1/2 cup
  • creamy ranch dressing: 1/4 cup
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • tomato slices: 2
  • cheddar cheese slices: 4
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1 teaspoon
